Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: ExifTool not found

Solution: Install with sudo apt install exiftool -y or sudo apt install libimage-exiftool-perl
Issue: Python library import errors

Solution: Install missing libraries: pip3 install PyPDF2 python-docx openpyxl
Issue: Permission denied when executing scripts

Solution: Make scripts executable: chmod +x script_name.py or chmod +x script_name.sh
Issue: Metadata still present after cleaning

Solution: Verify you used -overwrite_original flag with ExifTool, or check that Python scripts completed without errors
Issue: Batch processing skips files

Solution: Check file extensions match supported formats and verify file permissions
